Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.16,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}冲向深远的苍穹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.25,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:28.38,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在此刻生存 为此刻落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:34.01,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}言语空洞无力 是能够承受的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:39.77,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}有你相伴 就能超越时代变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:48.77,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在理解与理性将野性完全取代之前
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然聚集过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的战斗明明还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个目标就是美羽和我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种就过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们见识见识龙宫岛的实力！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十多只敌人接近 还有大批正陆续赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种状态下起飞太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不出去只会被敌群吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝试与基地管制塔联系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的Mir还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回归虚无去 Festum！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便消灭了我们 希望也会存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存活下去 并改变世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.32,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(700,500)\fs24\pos(900,613)}第９回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.32,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(700,500)\pos(1085,613)}两位英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的Mir还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊 保护通识者！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人朝机场去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰队被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办 光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该去巴尔卡还是机场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空战部队全都去机场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和陆战队去巴尔卡和卫队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算就凭你们那么点人对付阿撒谢尔型？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正横竖都打不倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们救出通识者后就撤往机场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也和你一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向真壁发过誓要保护他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！我们也一定会赶过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆路和水路都被堵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能往天上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 小艾 回头见！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我等你们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 在 那 里 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一眼就知道了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来！我可是第二代高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人在我们的内部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻挠部队的通信 召来了Festum的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明通识者中就有人能读取人心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个斯利那加地区都联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种非常事态下 还要我们按兵不动？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到的命令就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对那雷恩见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新联合国总部的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方舰队正在待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命？难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部队正在波利尼西亚空袭基地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(600,655)}Polynesia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部很可能对目标全域发布交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雷恩可是人类军不可或缺的人物！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情办完了？达斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(763,655)}Dustin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能也要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把机体都准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们阿耳戈斯小队出击的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(537,655)}Argos
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}注：阿耳戈斯 希腊神话中的百眼巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是某个基地被攻陷的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是要打谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人 还是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的工作自始至终都是解决那些被敌人同化的人 绮丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有可能把危害扩大的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一个人承受 也和我们倾诉倾诉呗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了现在还不知道要攻击谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要救助被同化的战友 结果却导致更多的部队被歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决不会让这样的事态再次发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那边的情况都那么危急了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是打算起飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是果敢的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机 掩护他们脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以珀耳修斯中队的名誉起誓 一定要保护希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是第一迎击队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将到达巴尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光弘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔特？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四卫队居然在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林区域已经被攻陷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(498,655)}forest block
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔特 你在哪 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出通识者是第一要务！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…恶魔出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…恶魔型…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(641,655)}Diablo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会被杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你 我要杀了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被包围的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些机体是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,识别代号还在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全装置发动了 没法攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人将森林区域卫队同化了 是恶魔型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全装置还有效是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体内置的芬里尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长机被控制了 连接不上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,删除机体识别代号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向交战中的部队发布交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交战规定α发布！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交战规定α 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认安全装置解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别打到自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么自相残杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…他们被敌人同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Warning Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中没有敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要钻进心里来了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱离不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我开枪 拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我…还没有失去自我之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 向我开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要取出驾驶座…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不应该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死在这种地方 不想死在龙宫岛之外的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我…还保有自我的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽要是再大一点就能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能很快做到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭 你已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是美羽能早点叫大哥哥他们来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步…？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行物接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度非常快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收到电波讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念出来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(插入曲)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛部队 加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 龙宫岛部队 加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D岛的…法芙娜…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是他们的城市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然被我猜中了 就是在一大群敌人里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你梦见和平的日子了吗 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…做了个美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体代号 Mk.Sein…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Nicht…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是总士前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以让他们恐惧的力量出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把敌人同化…吞噬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑前辈 果然了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你们来寻找的东西可能会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那或许就是我仍然活着的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…我的祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是被同化的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Nicht可能会把下面的人也一起抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给你了 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一半已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命体征…0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她活着 她还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半数存活 死亡的人也没有被同化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家全都复原了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被同化的机体恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求解除交战规定！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹的力量吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交战规定α解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复识别代号及安全装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧疏散市民和重建防线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这敌人是专攻驾驶座的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢 就这点能耐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要论同化能力 我也有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歪曲回转体的变形版吗 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(471,655)}worm sphere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D岛的「存在」与「虚无」的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(510,655)}Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(711,655)}Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}注：一骑与总士的机体名称在德语中的意思分别是「存在」与「虚无」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是救世主型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(701,655)}Salvator-model
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸想要开发的 拯救人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他开的这机体现在没有加装任何限制器…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保护不了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死驾驶员 抢夺机体的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是憎恨与虚无的凝结体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和Mk.Nicht一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我还不会被机体吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不搭理敌群了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只阿撒谢尔型和追踪岛的不是同一个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙想吞噬的就是这个城市的Mir吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十有八九
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就得保护这个Mir了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们始终出于同样的理由行使手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了生命 为了生存的家园
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了生而为人的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了安宁的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它们被剥夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护这一切免遭掠夺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地从敌人手中夺走一切
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
